title: TFW rito promises a free champ and you get a skin :(

embed.description: During Team Up Week, the community came together, partying up and giving gifts to hit 45.3 million, good enough to reach level 5. Head below to find a big list of everything you earned, and when you can expect it.

body:
Mystery Champion
Mystery Champion unlocked by 16:59 AEST on the 02/07 for all eligible players
You must link your Facebook and League accounts to unlock the Mystery Champ

I got a skin. I dont even have all the champions....

replies.body: I didn't recieve anything either, anyone heard anything new?
I didn't get anything at all and my Facebook is linked. :|

Apparently you have to link your facebook account by the 28th or something.

If not my friend had the same issue, he resolved it by just logging in and out again until he got the champion xD
